window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The Emperor is coming with a dragon, and we have two weeks to prepare.</b></p> <p>After defeating the Rhav and the Hive Queen, we thought winter would bring time to rest, rebuild, and advance our magical technology. But as the first snow fell, the Emperor appeared on the horizon with his armies.</p> <p>To make matters worse, the northern tribes of Utar have pledged him their blades. And Ash? She just learned the truth about my identity, and she’s not taking it well.</p> <p>Now, I must fortify the city, rally my people, and prepare for war on two fronts. Scout missions, high-stakes duels, and breakthrough spells are the only edge we have. But I know the Emperor. He wouldn’t march in winter unless he had cards left to play.</p> <p>There’s no more running.</p> <p>We’ll fight to finish the Revolution.</p>"; 
